description:
Solve as many mazes as possible before the time runs out.
Solve as many mazes as possible in before the time runs out.

Use d-pad style controls to move your character to the flag before the timer reaches 00:00. Mazes get more difficult as you progress.

This free and open source game is made with the Godot Game Engine. Minute Maze has no ads, no micro transactions, and can be played offline.
